name: ALBANIAN WATER FROG - ENDANGERED SPECIES SERIES #2 of 200
description: A series of 200 NFTs on Hic Et Nunc by Marc Craig of Endangered Species from countries around the world. The Albanian water frog is an endangered species and known populations are currently in decline. Significant threats to its habitat are presented by pollution and by drainage of wetlands, and a more direct threat is the aggressive collection of the species for commercial purposes.
